ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v22.message

Class ADT_A01

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractStructure
      • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractGroup
        • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractMessage
          • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v22.message.ADT_A01
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Group, Message, Structure, Visitable, Serializable

    public class ADT_A01
extends AbstractMessage

    Represents a ADT_A01 message structure (see chapter ?). This structure contains the following elements:

    • 1: MSH (MESSAGE HEADER)
    • 2: EVN (EVENT TYPE)
    • 3: PID (PATIENT IDENTIFICATION)
    • 4: NK1 (NEXT OF KIN) optional repeating
    • 5: PV1 (PATIENT VISIT)
    • 6: PV2 (PATIENT VISIT - additional information) optional
    • 7: OBX (OBSERVATION RESULT) optional repeating
    • 8: AL1 (PATIENT ALLERGY INFORMATION) optional repeating
    • 9: DG1 (DIAGNOSIS) optional repeating
    • 10: PR1 (PROCEDURES) optional repeating
    • 11: GT1 (GUARANTOR) optional repeating
    • 12: ADT_A01_INSURANCE (a Group object) optional repeating
    • 13: ACC (ACCIDENT) optional
    • 14: UB1 (UB82 DATA) optional
    • 15: UB2 (UB92 DATA) optional
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
